inline.description:
Email
————————————————————————————
1. Log in with email
2. Go to User menu > Profile > Profile Settings > Email > Edit
3. In "Confirm Email", enter the same thing as the existing primary email
4. Save
inline.expectedResult: Nothing happens (email remains the same, and does not need to be verified via email again).
